<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Cafe Locus — Café | Bakehouse | Pâtisserie</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  :root {
    --brown: #3E1C0D;
    --maroon: #6B1E1E;
    --cream: #F5ECD7;
    --warm-white: #FAF6EE;
    --gold: #C89B5A;
    --text-dark: #1A0A05;
    --text-muted: #7A6055;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--brown);
    color: var(--cream);
    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── NAV ── */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; z-index: 100;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 1.4rem 4rem;
    transition: background 0.4s, padding 0.4s;
  }
  nav.scrolled {
    background: rgba(30, 10, 4, 0.96);
    padding: 0.9rem 4rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--cream);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .nav-logo span { color: var(--gold); }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a {
    color: var(--cream);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.8;
    transition: opacity 0.3s, color 0.3s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { opacity: 1; color: var(--gold); }
  .nav-reserve {
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    color: var(--gold);
    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.55rem 1.4rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.3s, color 0.3s;
  }
  .nav-reserve:hover { background: var(--gold); color: var(--brown); }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 100vh;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--brown);
  }
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 60% 40%, rgba(107,30,30,0.35) 0%, transparent 65%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 80%, rgba(200,155,90,0.08) 0%, transparent 50%);
  }
  .hero-circle {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,155,90,0.15);
    animation: pulse-ring 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .hero-circle:nth-child(1) { width: 420px; height: 420px; }
  .hero-circle:nth-child(2) { width: 620px; height: 620px; animation-delay: 1s; opacity: 0.6; }
  .hero-circle:nth-child(3) { width: 820px; height: 820px; animation-delay: 2s; opacity: 0.3; }
  @keyframes pulse-ring {
    0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: var(--op, 1); }
    50% { transform: scale(1.04); opacity: calc(var(--op, 1) * 0.6); }
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
    text-align: center;
    animation: fade-up 1.2s ease both;
  }
  @keyframes fade-up {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.35em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fade-up 1s 0.3s ease both;
  }
  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(5rem, 12vw, 9rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 0.9;
    color: var(--cream);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fade-up 1s 0.5s ease both;
  }
  .hero-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold);
  }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(245,236,215,0.55);
    margin-top: 1.4rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fade-up 1s 0.7s ease both;
  }
  .hero-ctas {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    display: flex; gap: 1.2rem; justify-content: center;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fade-up 1s 0.9s ease both;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--brown);
    border: none;
    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.9rem 2.2rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { opacity: 0.85; }
  .btn-ghost {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--cream);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,236,215,0.3);
    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.9rem 2.2rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--gold); }

  .hero-scroll {
    position: absolute; bottom: 2.5rem; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(245,236,215,0.4);
    animation: fade-up 1s 1.2s ease both, bounce 2s 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
    opacity: 0;
  }
  .hero-scroll::after {
    content: '';
    width: 1px; height: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--gold), transparent);
  }
  @keyframes bounce {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(6px); }
  }

  /* ── SECTION COMMON ── */
  section { padding: 7rem 4rem; }
  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.35em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 5vw, 3.8rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--cream);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .section-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); }

  /* ── ABOUT ── */
  .about {
    background: #2A1208;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 6rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .about-visual {
    position: relative;
    height: 560px;
  }
  .about-frame {
    position: absolute;
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,155,90,0.25);
  }
  .about-frame:nth-child(1) {
    width: 75%; height: 82%;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    background: #3E1C0D;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .about-frame:nth-child(2) {
    width: 52%; height: 48%;
    bottom: 0; right: 0;
    background: var(--maroon);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }
  .about-frame-label {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(245,236,215,0.4);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1rem;
  }
  .about-stat {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 12%;
    left: 78%;
    background: var(--gold);
    padding: 1.2rem 1.4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .about-stat-num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--brown);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .about-stat-label {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--brown);
    margin-top: 0.3rem;
  }
  .about-text p {
    color: rgba(245,236,215,0.65);
    line-height: 1.9;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .about-tags {
    display: flex; gap: 0.8rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .about-tag {
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,155,90,0.35);
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
  }

  /* ── MENU PREVIEW ── */
  .menu-section {
    background: var(--brown);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .menu-section .section-label,
  .menu-section .section-title { text-align: center; }
  .menu-intro {
    color: rgba(245,236,215,0.55);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 1.2rem auto 3.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .menu-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: rgba(200,155,90,0.15);
    margin-top: 3rem;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;
  }
  .menu-card {
    background: #2A1208;
    padding: 2.8rem 2rem;
    text-align: left;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: background 0.4s;
    cursor: default;
  }
  .menu-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0;
    width: 100%; height: 2px;
    background: var(--gold);
    transform: scaleX(0); transform-origin: left;
    transition: transform 0.4s;
  }
  .menu-card:hover { background: #331510; }
  .menu-card:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }
  .menu-card-num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(200,155,90,0.12);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .menu-card-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }
  .menu-card-desc {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: rgba(245,236,215,0.5);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .menu-card-price {
    margin-top: 1.2rem;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  /* ── EXPERIENCE ── */
  .experience {
    background: var(--maroon);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    padding: 0;
    min-height: 560px;
  }
  .exp-text {
    padding: 7rem 4rem;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
  }
  .exp-text p {
    color: rgba(245,236,215,0.65);
    line-height: 1.9;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 420px;
  }
  .exp-info {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem;
  }
  .exp-info-row {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: rgba(245,236,215,0.6);
  }
  .exp-info-row::before {
    content: '';
    width: 24px; height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .exp-visual {
    background: #3E0D0D;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 6rem;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(200,155,90,0.1);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }
  .exp-visual-inner {
    position: absolute;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .exp-rating {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--gold);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .exp-rating-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(245,236,215,0.4);
  }
  .exp-stars {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  /* ── VISIT ── */
  .visit {
    background: #1A0A05;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .visit-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 3.5rem auto 0;
  }
  .visit-card {
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,155,90,0.2);
    padding: 2.2rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .visit-card-icon {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .visit-card-value {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--cream);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .visit-card-sub {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: rgba(245,236,215,0.4);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    background: #0D0503;
    padding: 3.5rem 4rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(200,155,90,0.12);
  }
  .footer-logo {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--cream);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }
  .footer-logo span { color: var(--gold); }
  .footer-tagline {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(245,236,215,0.3);
    margin-top: 0.3rem;
  }
  .footer-copy {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: rgba(245,236,215,0.25);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }
  .footer-contact {
    text-align: right;
  }
  .footer-contact a {
    display: block;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
  }
  .footer-contact a:hover { opacity: 0.7; }
  .footer-contact-label {
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(245,236,215,0.25);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  /* ── SCROLL REVEAL ── */
  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(28px);
    transition: opacity 0.9s ease, transform 0.9s ease;
  }
  .reveal.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: none;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav id="nav">
  <a class="nav-logo" href="#"><span>CAFE</span> LOCUS</a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#about">Story</a></li>
    <li><a href="#menu">Menu</a></li>
    <li><a href="#visit">Visit</a></li>
  </ul>
  <button class="nav-reserve" onclick="document.getElementById('visit').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Reserve</button>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero" id="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-circle"></div>
  <div class="hero-circle"></div>
  <div class="hero-circle"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">Café · Bakehouse · Pâtisserie</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title">CAFE<br/><em>LOCUS</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Coimbatore &nbsp;·&nbsp; Est. since</p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a class="btn-primary" href="#menu">Explore Menu</a>
      <a class="btn-ghost" href="#visit">Find Us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-scroll">Scroll</div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section class="about reveal" id="about">
  <div class="about-visual">
    <div class="about-frame">
      <p class="about-frame-label">Where every corner<br/>tells a story</p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-frame">
      <p class="about-frame-label">Crafted<br/>with care</p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-stat">
      <div class="about-stat-num">4.7</div>
      <div class="about-stat-label">Google Rating</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="about-text">
    <p class="section-label">Our Story</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">More than a café.<br/>A <em>gathering place.</em></h2>
    <p style="margin-top:1.5rem">Tucked into the heart of Coimbatore, Cafe Locus is where the aroma of freshly baked croissants meets the quiet hum of a city slowing down. We craft every plate and pour with intent.</p>
    <p>From our V60 pour-overs to our handmade pâtisserie, we believe good food is a form of care — for the people we serve, and the craft we practise.</p>
    <div class="about-tags">
      <span class="about-tag">Café</span>
      <span class="about-tag">Bakehouse</span>
      <span class="about-tag">Pâtisserie</span>
      <span class="about-tag">Specialty Coffee</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- MENU PREVIEW -->
<section class="menu-section" id="menu">
  <p class="section-label reveal">What we serve</p>
  <h2 class="section-title reveal">A menu built on <em>craft</em></h2>
  <p class="menu-intro reveal">Every item on our menu is made from scratch — baked in-house, sourced with care, served with intention.</p>
  <div class="menu-grid reveal">
    <div class="menu-card">
      <div class="menu-card-num">01</div>
      <div class="menu-card-title">Chicken Ham Croissant</div>
      <div class="menu-card-desc">Buttery, flaky, layered — filled with smoked chicken ham and aged cheese.</div>
      <div class="menu-card-price">From ₹ 380</div>
    </div>
    <div class="menu-card">
      <div class="menu-card-num">02</div>
      <div class="menu-card-title">V60 Pour Over</div>
      <div class="menu-card-desc">Single-origin beans, hand-poured to order. A ritual in every cup.</div>
      <div class="menu-card-price">From ₹ 260</div>
    </div>
    <div class="menu-card">
      <div class="menu-card-num">03</div>
      <div class="menu-card-title">Pâtisserie Selection</div>
      <div class="menu-card-desc">House-made tarts, eclairs, and seasonal pastries baked fresh daily.</div>
      <div class="menu-card-price">From ₹ 220</div>
    </div>
    <div class="menu-card">
      <div class="menu-card-num">04</div>
      <div class="menu-card-title">Locus Special</div>
      <div class="menu-card-desc">Our rotating chef's creation — ask your server what's on today.</div>
      <div class="menu-card-price">Seasonal</div>
    </div>
    <div class="menu-card">
      <div class="menu-card-num">05</div>
      <div class="menu-card-title">Food Plates</div>
      <div class="menu-card-desc">Thoughtfully composed plates for lunch and dinner — ₹400 to ₹1,400.</div>
      <div class="menu-card-price">From ₹ 400</div>
    </div>
    <div class="menu-card">
      <div class="menu-card-num">06</div>
      <div class="menu-card-title">Signature Drinks</div>
      <div class="menu-card-desc">Cold brews, matcha lattes, and house-made sodas crafted in-house.</div>
      <div class="menu-card-price">From ₹ 180</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- EXPERIENCE -->
<div class="experience reveal" id="experience">
  <div class="exp-text">
    <p class="section-label">The Locus Experience</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">A space to<br/><em>linger</em></h2>
    <p>Locus isn't just a café — it's a destination. Whether you're here for a solo morning pour-over or an evening out with people you love, we hold space for it all.</p>
    <div class="exp-info">
      <div class="exp-info-row">Open daily, 11:00 am – 10:30 pm</div>
      <div class="exp-info-row">Reservations welcome: +91 63696 35321</div>
      <div class="exp-info-row">Avinashi Road, Coimbatore — TN 641004</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="exp-visual">
    Locus
    <div class="exp-visual-inner">
      <div class="exp-rating">4.7</div>
      <div class="exp-stars">★ ★ ★ ★ ★</div>
      <div class="exp-rating-label">541 Google Reviews</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- VISIT -->
<section class="visit reveal" id="visit">
  <p class="section-label">Come find us</p>
  <h2 class="section-title">We're waiting <em>for you</em></h2>
  <div class="visit-grid">
    <div class="visit-card">
      <div class="visit-card-icon">Hours</div>
      <div class="visit-card-value">11:00 am<br/>– 10:30 pm</div>
      <div class="visit-card-sub">Open every day</div>
    </div>
    <div class="visit-card">
      <div class="visit-card-icon">Location</div>
      <div class="visit-card-value">D, 490–492<br/>Avinashi Road</div>
      <div class="visit-card-sub">Coimbatore, TN 641004</div>
    </div>
    <div class="visit-card">
      <div class="visit-card-icon">Reservations</div>
      <div class="visit-card-value">+91 63696<br/>35321</div>
      <div class="visit-card-sub">Call or WhatsApp</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer>
  <div>
    <div class="footer-logo"><span>CAFE</span> LOCUS</div>
